structure Equiv (α : Sort _) (β : Sort _) where
  protected toFun : α → β
  protected invFun : β → α
infixl:25 " ≃ " => Equiv
protected def Equiv.symm (e : α ≃ β) : β ≃ α := ⟨e.invFun, e.toFun⟩
end Mathlib.Logic.Equiv.Defs
